Gap: 0.065899
Exploitability: 16.47 mbb/g

Conclusions:
* Using all bets but one, all large bets could be removed without cost.
  But 3/4x hurt a little, 1/2x hurt some, and 1/4x hurt a lot.
* With three bets preflop and postflop, mb1b8p was best
    0.5/0.75/1.0 preflop; 0.25/0.5/1.5 postflop
  Exploitability@2000: 4.68 mbb/g
* With two bets preflop and postflop, mb1b8v was best
    0.5/0.75 preflop and 0.25/1.5 postflop
  Exploitability@2000: 9.28 mbb/g
* With three bets preflop and two postflop, mb1b8w is presumably best
    0.5/0.75/1.0 preflop and 0.25/1.5 postflop
  Exploitability@2000: 9.26 mbb/g
  No value to adding that 1.0x preflop bet
* With two bets preflop and three bets postflop, mb1b8x is presumably best
    0.5/0.75 preflop; 0.25/0.5/1.5 postflop
  Exploitability@2000: 4.71 mbb/g
  More confirmation that adding that 1.0x preflop bet is useless
  OTOH, adding that 0.5x postflop bet does help
* With one bet preflop and three bets post flop, mb1b8y presumably best
    0.5 preflop; 0.25/0.5/1.5 postflop
  Exploitability@2000: 9.24 mbb/g
  Real cost to removing the second preflop bet

