vs123a3
Two bets for opponent on preflop, one bet for us.
Three bets for opponent on flop
Three bets for us on flop, but last one can only be all-in
200:  Exploitability: 353.59 mbb/g
1000: Exploitability: 99.85 mbb/g
2000: Exploitability: 80.59 mbb/g
Barely better than vs1223.


Conclusions
* Only allowing one bet for ourselves preflop might be enough
* Only allowing one bet for ourselves on flop not enough
* Only allowing two bets for ourselves on flop not enough
* Only allowing one bet for ourselves on river not enough
